OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMyanmar overtakes          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FAfghanistan as top opium   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fproducer                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Myanmar is now the world's largest     
OL,6, producer of opium, overtaking          
OL,7, Afghanistan, a UN report says.         
OL,9,FIts opium production this year is      
OL,10,Festimated to rise by 36% to 1,080      
OL,11,Ftonnes, far ahead of the 330 tonnes    
OL,12,FAfghanistan reportedly produced.       
OL,14,FPoppy cultivation in Afghanistan       
OL,15,Fdropped by 95% after a drug ban by the 
OL,16,Fruling Taliban last year.              
OL,18,FMeanwhile, cultivation has expanded in 
OL,19,FMyanmar, where a brutal civil war, has 
OL,20,Fmade it a lucrative source of income.  
